'''Jabi Town''' was a [[Corellia/Legends|Corellian]] neighborhood in [[Corellian Quarter]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] after the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. It was subject to [[Galactic Alliance Guard]] raids during the [[Second Galactic Civil War]] in [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]].

